1. ipconfig 
ipconfig
ipconfig /all
ipconfig /release
ipconfig /renew
ipconfig /flushdns
  
2. ifconfig / ip 

ifconfig
sudo ifconfig eth0 down
sudo ifconfig eth0 up
3. ping
Test connectivity to another host.


ping 8.8.8.8
ping google.com
  
4. tracert / traceroute

tracert google.com    

5. netstat

netstat
netstat -an
netstat -r
  
6. nslookup

nslookup google.com
nslookup 8.8.8.8
  
7. dig
dig google.com
  
8. arp
arp -a
arp -d *
  
9. route
route print       # Windows
route -n  


10. telnet
telnet example.com 80
  
11. curl / wget

curl http://example.com
wget http://example.com

